to register to vote you: must be a united states citizen must be 18 years of age before the next election must be a resident of  for 30 days before the election locations: 1. county clerk's office, clinton county courthouse room 230, carlyle 2. most city and village clerk's offices, city and village halls 3. deputy registrars located throughout the county 4. drivers license facilities 5. mail-when registering by mail, you can not vote an absentee ballot for the first time only.